629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":359,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/08\/priorities-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":7335,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dawah: Priorities of Islam are faith, prayer, charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu'adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sent me to Yemen\u00a0and he said, \u201cVerily, you are going to people among the people of the Book, so call them to testify there is no God but Allah and I am the Messenger of Allah.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38447,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/11\/08\/akhirah-meeting-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":7335,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hereafter: Allah loves to meet His beloved","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 8, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever loves to meet Allah, Allah loves to meet him. Whoever hates to meet Allah, Allah hates to meet him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6508 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u06